name: BfROpenLab
body:
### What is BfROpenLab?
BfROpenLab is a collection of several extensions for the data analytics software KNIME ([http://www.knime.org/](http://www.knime.org/)) developed at the Federal Institute for Risk Assessment in Germany (BfR). It contains the following extensions:

* KNIME Foodchain Tracing Nodes
* KNIME GIS Nodes
* KNIME NLS Nodes
* SBML
